senses.sense_definition: Able to be put into something else.

examples.text: The memory card is easily <w>insertable</w> into the slot on the side of the camera.
Doctors recommended an <w>insertable</w> cardiac monitor to track the patient's heart rhythm.

senses.sense_definition: Something that is designed to be put inside something else, often a medical device.

examples.text: The hospital stocks various medical <w>insertables</w> for patient care.
These <w>insertables</w> are made from safe materials to prevent allergic reactions.
